I"|<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Git flow : lu·ªìng ƒëi qu·∫£n l&yacute; source code trong d·ª± &aacute;n</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Branch : C&aacute;c nh&aacute;nh m&agrave; m&igrave;nh t·∫°o ra (master,hotfix,release,Develop,feature)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- pull request (PR): t·∫°o 1 y&ecirc;u c·∫ßu cho leader review code tr∆∞·ªõc khi merge</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Review: xem code</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Merge : ƒë·∫©y code v&agrave;o kho</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Release (staging) :m&ocirc;i tr∆∞·ªùng cho kh </span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- c&aacute;c l·ªánh thao t&aacute;c vs git nh∆∞ thao t&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n lilux (cd/mkdir/rm/rm -Rf/vi/pwd)</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">------------------------Repository------------------</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">L·ªánh c·∫•u h&igrave;nh T&ecirc;n v&agrave; Email</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">git config --global user.name "T&ecirc;n c·ªßa b·∫°n"</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">git config --global user.email "Email c·ªßa b·∫°n"</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Ki·ªÉm tra l·∫°i config xem ƒë&atilde; ƒë&uacute;ng ch∆∞a</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">git config --list</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">---------------------------------------------------</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">x&oacute;a nh&aacute;nh :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">git branch -d &lt;t&ecirc;n nh&aacute;nh&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">git branch -D &lt;t&ecirc;n nh&aacute;nh&gt; : quy·∫øt ƒë·ªãnh x&oacute;a b·∫•t ch·∫•p th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng "-D"</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-------------------------------------------------</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- s·ª≠a commit b·ªã nh·∫ßm:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+ git commit --amend </span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Undo l·∫°i commit:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+ Undo l·∫°i 1 file : git checkout -- [d∆∞·ªùng d·∫´n + t&ecirc;n file]</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+ undo 1 commit m&agrave; mu·ªën gi·ªØ l·∫°i nh·ªØng th·ª© ƒë&atilde; thay ƒë·ªïi :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> - git reset --soft HEAD~1</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+ undo 1 commit m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng mu·ªën gi·ªØ l·∫°i nh·ªØng th·ª© ƒë&atilde; thay ƒë·ªïi :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> - git reset --hard HEAD~1</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- git clean : git clean --force</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">- Git clone th&ocirc;ng qua SSH</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ssh-keygen -t rsa</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-------------------------------------------------------</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-L∆∞u l·∫°i tr·∫°ng th&aacute;i hi·ªán t·∫°i c·ªßa branch :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ git stash save</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-L∆∞u l·∫°i to&agrave;n b·ªô tr·∫°ng th&aacute;i hi·ªán t·∫°i c·ªßa branch :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">M·ªói l·∫ßn l∆∞u s·∫Ω t·∫°o th&agrave;nh 1 version t·∫°i th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÉm ƒë&oacute;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Xem l·∫°i danh s&aacute;ch ƒë&atilde; l∆∞u :</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ git stash list</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-N·∫øu mu·ªën xem c·∫£ n·ªôi dung c·ªßa t·ª´ng thay ƒë·ªïi th&igrave; th&ecirc;m option -p</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; $ git stash list -p</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-ho·∫∑c xem n·ªôi dung c·ª• th·ªÉ h∆°n n·ªØa c·ªßa l·∫ßn thay ƒë·ªïi th·ª© 1:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; $ git stash show stash@{1}</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-L·∫•y l·∫°i thay ƒë·ªïi:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; $ git stash apply stash@{1}</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-X&oacute;a:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; $ git stash drop</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">-Cherry-pick d&ugrave;ng ƒë·ªÉ l·∫•y commit t·ª´ nh&aacute;nh n&agrave;y sang nh&aacute;nh kh&aacute;c:</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;$ git cherry-pick [ID-commit]</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">C&aacute;ch x·ª≠ l&yacute; c&aacute;c l·ªói th∆∞·ªùng g·∫∑p trong git</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">ƒê·∫ßu ti&ecirc;n mu·ªën s·ª≠a ƒë∆∞·ª£c l·ªói trong git ta ph·∫£i th·ª±c hi·ªán t·∫°o ra n&oacute; tr∆∞·ªõc ƒë&atilde;. Ph·∫ßn 1 s·∫Ω n&oacute;i 1 s·ªë l·ªánh c∆° b·∫£n trong git theo follow t·∫°o v&agrave; s·ª≠ d·ª•ng 1 project.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">- git tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y scm l&agrave; git local&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">- github,gitlab&nbsp; l&agrave; git remote</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">C&aacute;c l·ªánh c∆° b·∫£n</span></strong></span></p>
<p><br /><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">1. Kh·ªüi t·∫°o git</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># Ch·∫Øc ai c≈©ng bi·∫øt r·ªìi mu·ªën kh·ªüi t·∫°o 1 repo ta d&ugrave;ng l·ªánh</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">&nbsp;<span style="color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git init</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">2. Th&ecirc;m m·ªõi remote v&agrave;o project</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># hi·ªÉn th·ªã danh s&aacute;ch remote trong git c·ªßa project </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; git remote -v</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># Th&ecirc;m m·ªõi m·ªôt remote v&agrave;o git</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; git remote add origin &lt;url&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">3. Clone project</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">B·∫°n ph&aacute;t hi·ªán ra l&agrave; b·∫°n ƒë&atilde; c&oacute; url c·ªßa project s·∫µn r·ªìi th&igrave; t·ªôi g&igrave; ph·∫£i kh·ªüi t·∫°o git m·ªõi n·ªØa. Thay v&agrave;o ƒë&oacute; h&atilde;y d&ugrave;ng clone</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; git clone</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong>4. L&agrave;m vi·ªác c&ugrave;ng branch</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Git</span> </strong>l&agrave; m·ªôt h·ªá th·ªëng qu·∫£n l&yacute; phi&ecirc;n b·∫£n ph&acirc;n t&aacute;n, v&igrave; th·∫ø m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh c·ªßa n&oacute; gi·ªëng nh∆∞ m·ªôt c&aacute;i c&acirc;y. V·∫≠y b·∫°n c&oacute; th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n ra lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; m·ªói c&aacute;i c&acirc;y lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; m·ªôt th&acirc;n c&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh, v&agrave; c&aacute;c c&agrave;nh, nh&aacute;nh nh·ªè. T∆∞∆°ng t·ª± trong git ta c&oacute; branch th·ªÉ hi·ªán m·ªói nh&aacute;nh nh·ªè c·ªßa m·ªôt c&aacute;i c&acirc;y v&agrave; nh&aacute;nh ch&iacute;nh t∆∞∆°ng ƒë∆∞∆°ng v·ªõi th&acirc;n c&acirc;y th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l&agrave; master. N·∫øu t·ª´ng l&agrave;m vi·ªác th·ª±c t·∫ø trong c&aacute;c d·ª± &aacute;n b·∫°n th∆∞·ªùng th·∫•y nh&aacute;nh master s·∫Ω l&agrave; nh&aacute;nh r·ªóng, thay v&agrave;o ƒë&oacute; nh·ªØng developer s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c&aacute;c nh&aacute;nh c&oacute; t&ecirc;n nh∆∞ development, product, test,.... ƒêi·ªÅu n&agrave;y gi&uacute;p cho c&aacute;c l·∫≠p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ph&acirc;n bi·ªán v&agrave; thao t&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n nh·ªØng m&ocirc;i tr∆∞·ªùng t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng quan qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri·ªÉn ph·∫ßn m·ªÅm m·ªôt c&aacute;ch d·ªÖ d&agrave;ng v&agrave; minh b·∫°ch h∆°n.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><img class="" style="width: 30%; height: auto;" src="https://images.viblo.asia/3b171116-23fb-4bd2-a8ac-65b63fe65372.png" alt="" width="600" height="779" /></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">M·ªôt s·ªë l·ªánh c∆° b·∫£n</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # Danh s&aacute;ch branch</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git branch</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># t·∫°o m·ªõi branch</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git branch (&lt;name&gt;)</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># Di chuy·ªÉn t·ª´ branch hi·ªán t·∫°i ƒë·∫øn m·ªôt branch kh&aacute;c b·∫±ng t&ecirc;n branch ƒë&oacute;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git checkout &lt;name&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"># T·∫°o v&agrave; di chuy·ªÉn t·ª´ branch hi·ªán t·∫°i ƒë·∫øn m·ªôt branch m·ªõi</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git checkout -b &lt;name&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> ```markdown</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">**5. H·ª£p nh·∫•t branch**</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> - ƒê&acirc;y l&agrave; m·ªôt trong nh·ªØng c&acirc;u l·ªánh c∆° b·∫£n th∆∞·ªùng d&ugrave;ng c·ªßa quy tr&igrave;nh. Nh∆∞ng v·ªõi vi·ªác c&aacute;c tool h·ªó tr·ª£ nh∆∞ github, gitlab,... th&igrave; vi·ªác s·ª≠ d·ª•ng c&acirc;u l·ªánh n&agrave;y ch·ªâ c&ograve;n n·∫±m ·ªü d∆∞·ªõi local m&agrave; th&ocirc;i.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">``` shell</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> - ƒë·ªÉ h·ª£p nh·∫•t nh&aacute;nh branch-name v&agrave;o nh&aacute;nh master</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git merge &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">6. C·∫≠p nh·∫≠t code m·ªõi nh·∫•t v·ªÅ</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Khi l&agrave;m vi·ªác m·ªôt m&igrave;nh th·ª±c t·∫ø b·∫°n s·∫Ω kh&ocirc;ng c·∫ßn ƒë·∫øn git nh∆∞ng khi l&agrave;m vi·ªác nh&oacute;m v&agrave; mu·ªën l·∫•y code m·ªõi nh·∫•t t·ª´ m·ªôt nh&aacute;nh n&agrave;o ƒë&oacute; tr&ecirc;n repo online v·ªÅ th&igrave; b·∫°n s·∫Ω d&ugrave;ng l·ªánh sau:</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git pull origin &lt;branch&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">7. xem status v&agrave; m·ªôt v&agrave;i th·ª© n·ªØa</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git status</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git diff &ndash;-stat</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Nh·ªØng s·ª± c·ªë th∆∞·ªùng g·∫∑p trong Git</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">1. Vi·∫øt sai message commit</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">ƒê·ªÉ thay ƒë·ªïi n·ªô dung commit, th&ecirc;m, s·ª≠a file v&agrave;o commit r·∫•t ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n b·∫°n ch·ªâ c·∫ßn s·ª≠ d·ª•ng</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git commit --amend</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">2. ƒê·∫∑t sai t&ecirc;n branch</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Vi·ªác g&otilde; nh·∫ßm hay thi·∫øt th&agrave;nh ph·∫ßn theo convention khi ƒë·∫∑t t&ecirc;n branch l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng hi·∫øm. L&uacute;c m·ªõi ti·∫øp c·∫≠n b·∫°n th∆∞·ªùng l·ª±a ch·ªçn gi·∫£i ph&aacute;p l&agrave; t·∫°o m·ªôt branch m·ªõi. C&oacute; m·ªôt c&aacute;ch nhanh h∆°n r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu gi·ªëng nh∆∞ rename trong c&aacute;c ph·∫ßn l&agrave;m vi·ªác v·ªõi file ƒë&oacute; l&agrave; d&ugrave;ng c&acirc;u l·ªánh:</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git branch -m &lt;t&ecirc;n branch sau khi ƒë·ªïi&gt;</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">3. Commit ch∆°i ch∆°i v&agrave; gi·ªù mu·ªën n&oacute; bay m&agrave;u</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Vi·ªác l&agrave;m ng·ªëc ng·∫øch n&agrave;y di·ªÖn ra th∆∞·ªùng xuy&ecirc;n trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh l&agrave;m vi·ªác, v·∫≠y l&agrave;m th·∫