<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Git</span> gi·ªØ m·ªôt con tr·ªè ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát c&oacute; t&ecirc;n HEAD. Trong Git, ƒë&acirc;y l&agrave; m·ªôt con tr·ªè t·ªõi nh&aacute;nh n·ªôi b·ªô m&agrave; b·∫°n ƒëang l&agrave;m vi·ªác</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Tr&ecirc;n Git, nh·ªØng th∆∞ m·ª•c ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·∫∑t trong s·ª± qu·∫£n l&yacute; c·ªßa Git m&agrave; m·ªçi ng∆∞·ªùi ƒëang th·ª±c hi·ªán c&ocirc;ng vi·ªác trong th·ª±c t·∫ø ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l&agrave; working tree.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Gi·ªØa repository v&agrave; working tree t·ªìn t·∫°i m·ªôt n∆°i g·ªçi l&agrave; index. Index l&agrave; n∆°i ƒë·ªÉ chu·∫©n b·ªã cho vi·ªác commit l&ecirc;n repository</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">C&aacute;ch 1: S·ª≠ d·ª•ng reset (khi ch∆∞a c&oacute; ai pull v·ªÅ)</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git reset HEAD~</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Di chuy·ªÉn HEAD v·ªÅ v·ªã tr&iacute; commit reset v&agrave; v·∫´n gi·ªØ nguy&ecirc;n t·∫•t c·∫£ c&aacute;c thay ƒë·ªïi c·ªßa file, nh∆∞ng lo·∫°i b·ªè c&aacute;c thay ƒë·ªïi kh·ªèi stage (ƒê∆∞a HEAD v&agrave; index v·ªÅ nh∆∞ c≈©)</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git reset {commit_id}</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git reset --hard HEAD~</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Di chuy·ªÉn con tr·ªè HEAD v·ªÅ v·ªã tr&iacute; commit reset v&agrave; lo·∫°i b·ªè t·∫•t c·∫£ s·ª± thay ƒë·ªïi c·ªßa file sau th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÉm commit reset</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">HEAD~ c&oacute; &yacute; nghƒ©a gi·ªëng v·ªõi HEAD^ hay @^, nghƒ©a l&agrave; quay v·ªÅ tr∆∞·ªõc 1 commit</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Mu·ªën quay v·ªÅ tr∆∞·ªõc n commit, </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">VD 5 commit th&igrave; c&oacute; th·ªÉ thay b·∫±ng HEAD~5.</span></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">--hard c&oacute; nghƒ©a l&agrave; b·ªè commit ƒëi v&agrave; b·ªè c·∫£ nh·ªØng thay ƒë·ªïi ch∆∞a ƒë∆∞·ª£c commit trong working space. Khi n&agrave;y m&ocirc;i tr∆∞·ªùng s·∫Ω ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n "s·∫°ch s·∫Ω" nh∆∞ th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÉm tr∆∞·ªõc khi commit</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git reset --soft HEAD~</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">L·ªánh n&agrave;y ch·ªâ di chuy·ªÉn HEAD v·ªÅ v·ªã tr&iacute; commit reset. Tr·∫°ng th&aacute;i c·ªßa stage v&agrave; t·∫•t c·∫£ s·ª± thay ƒë·ªïi c·ªßa file s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c gi·ªØ nguy&ecirc;n</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">--soft c&oacute; nghƒ©a l&agrave; b·ªè commit ƒëi nh∆∞ng gi·ªØ nguy&ecirc;n nh·ªØng thay ƒë·ªïi ch∆∞a ƒë∆∞·ª£c commit trong working space.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">--soft h·ªØu d·ª•ng khi b·∫°n mu·ªën gi·ªØ l·∫°i nh·ªØng thay ƒë·ªïi ch∆∞a commit cho l·∫ßn commit ti·∫øp theo</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">C&aacute;ch 2: S·ª≠ d·ª•ng revert (ng∆∞·ªùi kh&aacute;c ƒë&atilde; pull v·ªÅ)</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # commit_hash l&agrave; m&atilde; commit</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git revert &lt;commit_hash&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">C&aacute;ch 3: S·ª≠ d·ª•ng --amend</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git commit --amend</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # B·∫°n c&oacute; th·ªÉ s·ª≠ d·ª•ng l·ªánh n&agrave;y ƒë·ªÉ vi·∫øt l·∫°i commit message</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # Option --no-edit s·ª≠ d·ª•ng khi b·∫°n ch·ªâ mu·ªën th&ecirc;m file m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng mu·ªën s·ª≠a commit message</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;git commit --amend --no-edit</span><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">4. Khi l·ª° tay commit nh·∫ßm sang m·ªôt branch kh&aacute;c</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">C&oacute; nh·ªØng l&uacute;c ta s∆° su·∫•t l·ª° tay commit th·∫≥ng v&agrave;o master trong khi th·ª±c ra l&agrave; mu·ªën commit v&agrave;o m·ªôt branch kh&aacute;c</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> #ƒê·∫ßu ti&ecirc;n l&agrave; t·∫°o m·ªôt branch kh&aacute;c ch·ª©a tr·∫°ng th&aacute;i m&agrave; ta ƒë&atilde; commit</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;$ git branch other-branch</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> #ƒê∆∞a HEAD, index c·ªßa master v·ªÅ 1 commit tr∆∞·ªõc ƒë&oacute;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;$ git reset --hard HEAD~</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> #Check out sang branch c&oacute; commit tr∆∞·ªõc ƒë&oacute;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;$ git checkout other-branch</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">5. G·ªôp nhi·ªÅu commit th&agrave;nh m·ªôt commit</span></strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">S·ª≠ d·ª•ng rebase + squash (or fixup) ƒë·ªÉ t·ªïng h·ª£p l·∫°i c&aacute;c commit c≈©</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Squash: gi·ªØa nguy&ecirc;n commit message c·ªßa nh·ªØng commit tr∆∞·ªõc</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;">Fixup: xo&aacute; commit message c·ªßa nh·ªØng commit tr∆∞·ªõc</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> Rebase v·ªÅ n commit tr∆∞·ªõc (c&oacute; bao g·ªìm c·∫£ HEAD)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # (V&iacute; d·ª•) git rebase -i HEAD~3</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp;$ git rebase -i HEAD~&lt;s·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng commit&gt;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # Sau l·ªánh n&agrave;y s·∫Ω m·ªü ra editor n&ecirc;n h&atilde;y s·ª≠a l·∫°i nh∆∞ sau r·ªìi l∆∞u l·∫°i</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif; color: #ff0000;"> # Note: V·ªõi vim b·∫•m &ldquo;a&rdquo; ƒë·ªÉ b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu edit &rarr; B·∫•m ECS ƒë·ªÉ d·ª´ng thao t&aacute;c edit &rarr; B·∫•m &ldquo;shift + z + z&rdquo; ƒë·ªÉ save</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # (tr∆∞·ªõc khi s·ª≠a) c&aacute;c commit c≈© t·ª´ tr&ecirc;n xu·ªëng d∆∞·ªõi</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> pick aa11bbc commit message 1</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> pick b2c3c4d commit message 2</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> pick 4e56fgh commit message 3</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> „Éª„Éª„Éª</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;"> # (sau khi s·ª≠a) c&aacute;c commit tr∆∞·ªõc l&agrave; squash s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·ªïng h·ª£p v&agrave;o 1 commit ·ªü ƒ